      button or link and a "modal" element that toggles visibility.
    </p>
    <blockquote class="blockquote blockquote-info">
      <h1>Note</h1>
      <p>The modal element is `position: absolute` so it will be positioned
      relative to it's parent.</p>
      <p>Ensure that the trigger and modal elements are under
      under a `.popover-wrapper` element.</p>
      <code class="language-markup">{{#raw}}<div class="popover-wrapper">
  <a href="#" data-role="popover" data-target="example-popover">Open popover</a>
  <div class="popover-body"> ... </div>
</div>{{/raw}}</code>
    </blockquote>

    <p>Demo</p>
